Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:44.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}のばした手のひら 舞い降りたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:59.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}行き交う船 しぶきを上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:06.71,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}懐かしい 君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}会いたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:18.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}遥か遠く離れてる時も
